2025-11-28 12:39:57 - StudioAtrium\Entity\User\Message:Update {"timestamp":1764333597,"user_id":18915,"user_ip":"109.95.116.11","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit\/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome\/142.0.0.0 Safari\/537.36","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\User\\Message\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_update","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\User\\Message","entity_data":{"id":1456,"__foreign_props":[],"user_id":"18915","parent_id":"1455","author":"Studio Atrium","title":"Re: Aurora Maxi","message":"<p>Dzie\u0144 dobry Panie Marcinie<\/p>\r\n<p>W projekcie Aurora Maxi przewidziano strop lekki drewniany, czyli podwieszany sufit przymocowany na wieszakach metalowych do konstrukcji wi\u0119\u017aby.<\/p>\r\n<p>W za\u0142\u0105czniku do wiadomo\u015bci do\u0142\u0105czam materia\u0142y.<\/p>\r\n<p>W przypadku dodatkowych pyta\u0144, pozostaj\u0119 w kontakcie.<\/p>\r\n<p>Pozdrawiam<br \/>\u0141ukasz Jakubiec<\/p>","create_date":"2025-11-28 13:35:54","status":"read","attachments":{"UserMessageFile":[{"id":52222,"__foreign_props":[],"profile_name":"UserMessageFile","filename":"6929976248de9-gl_1172-wt21-pb21-aurora_maxi-zestawienia_q.pdf","path":"36\/372772","title":"Zestawienie materia\u0142\u00f3w","description":"","owner_uid":"372772","props":{"original_filename":"GL 1172-WT21-PB21-Aurora Maxi-zestawienia_q.pdf","file_size":551019,"file_created":1764333410},"sorting":0,"parent_attachment_id":0,"parent_relationship":"","_uid":13368837,"childAttachments":[]},{"id":52223,"__foreign_props":[],"profile_name":"UserMessageFile","filename":"6929977128f39-gl_1172a-wt21-pb21-aurora_maxi-fundament_q.pdf","path":"36\/372772","title":"Rzut fundament\u00f3w","description":"","owner_uid":"372772","props":{"original_filename":"GL 1172A-WT21-PB21-Aurora Maxi-fundament_q.pdf","file_size":375096,"file_created":1764333425},"sorting":"1","parent_attachment_id":0,"parent_relationship":"","_uid":13369093,"childAttachments":[]},{"id":